1. START
   │
2. ADF Lookup Activity
   ├── Query: SELECT schema and table names
   └── Output: Table list from SalesLT schema
   │
3. ForEach Activity (Loop through tables)
   ├── Parameter: Current table name
   └── Execute: Copy Activity
       │
4. Copy Activity
   ├── Source: SQL Server table
   └── Sink: ADLS Bronze/{schema}/{table}/
   │
5. Databricks Notebook - Bronze to Silver
   ├── Read: Parquet from Bronze
   ├── Transform: DateTime to Date conversion
   └── Write: Delta format to Silver
   │
6. Databricks Notebook - Silver to Gold
   ├── Read: Delta from Silver
   ├── Transform: Column renaming
   └── Write: Delta format to Gold
   │
7. END
